      "body": "Guilherme Cortes: Hi Ruggero, let me pass this feedback to the team.\n\nRegarding notifications, it looks like all admins are subscribed to these notifications by default, but you can configure whether you receive email alerts in the profile > notification tab here:\nhttps://dashboard.getstream.io/user/notifications\n\n---\n\n\n> Slack thread from **#yoobic_stream**. This message was sent via Thena",
      "html_body": "<div class=\"zd-comment\" dir=\"auto\">Guilherme Cortes: Hi Ruggero, let me pass this feedback to the team.<br><br>Regarding notifications, it looks like all admins are subscribed to these notifications by default, but you can configure whether you receive email alerts in the profile &gt; notification tab here:<br><a href=\"https://dashboard.getstream.io/user/notifications\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://dashboard.getstream.io/user/notifications</a><br><br>---<br><br><blockquote> Slack <a href=\"https://getstream.slack.com/archives/C04N9RP7LUF/p1776447046249179?thread_ts=1776446542.211569&amp;cid=C04N9RP7LUF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">thread</a> from <b>#yoobic_stream</b>. This message was sent via Thena</blockquote></div>",
